name: Curious Cats #0021
description: It is said that cats came from outer space, a parallel universe as ours, the universe predominantly inhibited by Cats! In that Cativerse, cats are the master race. Each cat is an individual, a person, each comprises a unique character. Full of catily emotions of love, hate, anger, playfullness and sadness. They have a great variation in the way of life, from Primitive to Advanced, they are at various stages of chain.
